snippet.title: Formicide Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/434510

Formicide is a fast-paced 2D online platformer with a lineup of versatile classes. Think Worms meets Team Fortress 2. Face off with teammates against enemies in destructible environments with the weapons and abilities at your disposal. Free on Steam!
